WEBVTT

1
01:09:39.170 --> 01:09:41.460 
但是  我会建议你多休息
But I would suggest plenty of rest

2
01:09:41.510 --> 01:09:45.550 
并且多晒晒太阳
and lots and lots of sunshine.

3
01:09:46.300 --> 01:09:48.510 
我恨阳光
I hate sunshine.

4
01:09:48.560 --> 01:09:52.730 
我恨可怕的  可恶的太阳
I hate horrible, wholesome sunshine!

5
01:09:52.810 --> 01:09:54.520 
我恨它  我恨它
I hate it, I hate it!

6
01:09:54.560 --> 01:09:57.150 
我恨它  我恨它  恨它
I hate, hate, hate...

7
01:09:57.560 --> 01:10:01.530 
你真的很棒  梅林  但  但你差点没命
You were really great, Merlin. But you could have been killed.

8
01:10:01.570 --> 01:10:04.780 
如果你从中学到了什么的话  那就值得了
It was worth it, lad, if you learned something from it.

9
01:10:05.910 --> 01:10:08.280 
知识和智慧是真正的力量
Knowledge and wisdom is the real power.

10
01:10:08.370 --> 01:10:12.000 
轮到你了  沃特  现在继续你的学习  孩子
Right you are, Wart. So, stick to your schooling, boy.

